title: Barbie
star: Margot Robbie Ryan Gosling Will Ferrell Michael Cera
header_pra: Barbie and Ken are having the time of their lives in the colorful and seemingly perfect world of Barbie Land. However, when they get a chance to go to the real world, they soon discover the joys and perils of living among humans.

title: Xtreme
star: Teo García, Óscar Jaenada, Óscar Casas, Andrea Duro
header_pra: Two years after the murder of his son and father, a retired hitman sets in motion a carefully crafted revenge plan against the killer: his own brother. title: The Ghazi Attack
star: Rana Daggubati, Taapsee Pannu, Kay Kay Menon, Atul Kulkarni and Satya Dev
header_pra: Almost on the verge of declaring war, the naval forces of India and Pakistan are involved in a deadly duel. Amid this confusion, a Pakistani stealth submarine PNS Ghazi embarks on a secret mission.
